{"tid":97961,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭只係稻草人要黎吸嬲，曾俊華先係真","createTime":"2017-01-28T05:12:49.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-09T03:00:45.000Z","uid":22054,"like":14,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"c440c917ec5c16dd49505e0ab8e5a9a6b7dbb240","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:12:49.000Z","msg":"如果得曾俊華一個對其他人（胡國興又好邊個民主派都好）曾俊華有咩都一定要硬接<br />\n<br />\n但出多個林鄭「繼承梁振英」就唔唔同，民主派唔敢出人，出都俾人屌到化，同時將一個冇人理「選舉」變成好多人理<br />\n<br />\n而家全港既怨氣俾曬林鄭都唔夠，仲要日日爭住出黎柒，令到曾俊華立廿三條、831呢D都有人幫佢解釋「為入閘姐，到時唔會咁」<br />\n<br />\n一舊中共欽點既屎，而家推多舊更臭既出黎，原本果舊就會由屎一舊變成人人心目中既救星。何樂而不為？"},{"pid":"60c7bbdc6e21f441d90f701e5bc09385b45b20ed","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:24:59.000Z","msg":"冇人理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51f3e188643572df9e92137ce9c86bb5945b4f6","tid":97961,"uid":23544,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:26:38.000Z","msg":"學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c04c5b3c88be524bb3d0ffc9e8a5497ec849fb16","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:29:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唐唐係大地產商，繼承曾蔭權路線，梁振英打大老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e6c3d0f90368af939c095a52f9163838d4c5570","tid":97961,"uid":53524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:30:26.000Z","msg":"same idea,  幫push"},{"pid":"baff09682c424e4f6509c2892a6508b041d25721","tid":97961,"uid":71008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:34:12.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>學到野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唐唐係大地產商，繼承曾蔭權路線，梁振英打大老虎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同俾d時間習總冇分別"},{"pid":"39809cf084c79849ed12a8e7b567336309ba5f52","tid":97961,"uid":46849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:35:21.000Z","msg":"留名等睇薯片連入閘都唔夠票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ecb20aab1b9749509b42edd4aa259f3965d0191","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:41:39.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>留名等睇薯片連入閘都唔夠票 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係商界都夠入啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 到時開票一定大炒淋病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1fcd6feb893369f249a313035bdcc43ab90cde43","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:50:56.000Z","msg":"四年前一大班左膠同「知識分子」中伏，屌柒唐英年同時幫梁振英抬轎，四年後既2016只係換左人，劇情不變<br />\n<br />\n咁係咪應該要屌曾俊華？唔係，只要唔理、唔講今次選舉就得喇"},{"pid":"e10f3a0d65082fe584c7835c685a1610e71bfa39","tid":97961,"uid":23392,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T05:54:28.000Z","msg":"林鄭真係出黎日日搏嬲"},{"pid":"c4dce216b049e6bed4d2e23f55b1268488f6baf4","tid":97961,"uid":22054,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-28T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>林鄭真係出黎日日搏嬲</blockquote><br />\n當年唐英年場戲未必假得曬，但今年真係好劇本，換句話說今年仲衰過4年前<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n如果今年真係得既話4年後可能梁振英復出/用張志肛果d去陪跑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5300360edb5d6194214cfd9e258bfcf74c2f12d","tid":97961,"uid":294,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23:22:10.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>same idea,  幫push</blockquote>"},{"pid":"02307fc02a11abe299aca1f9b7886fffb022e883","tid":97961,"uid":24730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-08T23: